Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.43,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.61,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,the guys that appear in this anime\Nare delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:08.32,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please do not, under any circumstances,\Nimitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.36,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(320,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:24.16,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:24.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason l am crying is\Nbecause l am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:29.59,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:29.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:34.88,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:34.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:40.47,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:40.47,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:45.73,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:45.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.98,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.98,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:52.33,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:52.33,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:59.18,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:59.18,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.80,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.80,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:09.24,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:09.24,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.21,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.21,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.92,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:20.72,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:20.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:30.52,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(316,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&HB5B1CB&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:30.61,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(316,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&HA379B0&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.82,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(316,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&H884994&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:43.62,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Des-High Year 1 Boss Noboru Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.66,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,An excellent leader needs an excellent council.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:41.36,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fact that I didn't have a capable No. 2 until now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.62,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,is also the reason our school has been stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:48.62,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,It can also be said that it's because there was\Nno one who met my standards for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:53.46,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally found the man\Nwho's suitable to be No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.14,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Yamaguchi accepted this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:58.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,that probably means he's no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.58,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:04.11,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't get rattled.\NHe's actually here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.69,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.23,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\pos(325,390)}Akira Nakao (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:11.06,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do? I'm Akira Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.15,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Mick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:14.15,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mick. Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.99,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He's No. 2 from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.36,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.64,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll knock you guys\N down with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.18,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.30,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:31.88,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be good\N if you work on your timing a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.88,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.75,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't call a ventriloquist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishikawa's jaw is dislocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.66,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something like "ventriloquist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:49.70,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you gotta say things\N that destroy people's dreams, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.53,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, when Americans see magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:57.71,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,they enjoy it purely as entertainment\Neven if they know it's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.34,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the Japanese see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.74,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,they immediately try to uncover\Nthe tricks and gimmicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.61,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say the same thing about pro wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:09.62,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's staged, have a mind that\Nenjoys it purely as entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.42,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.52,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:17.59,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamaguchi, I don't \Nmean to tease or stir things up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:21.06,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but can I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.83,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is No. 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:29.27,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Even I hadn't thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:33.24,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll ask. Which one is No. 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.68,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to ask him, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.75,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Mick, we've been together for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:42.05,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like only one of us\Ncan become No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.72,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Of course I'm No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:51.86,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this? \NOne of you is "No." and the other is "2".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.10,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So put together you're No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.70,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll use that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.50,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,The joke's a little old, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.76,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.64,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are a trio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.14,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.22,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of Tokyo Comic Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.89,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.98,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:14.22,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but I imagine he's \Npowerful enough to be No. 2, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:16.40,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we won't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you don't know\Nhis real power yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.43,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just a variety guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.06,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.19,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.23,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the puppets off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.83,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really no ordinary guy after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.33,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? My voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.74,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.57,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Delayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.62,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?! Just like\Nsatellite coverage, right?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.75,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.76,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,To say the least, \Nthis doesn't help in fighting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:05:01.56,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he's No. 2 from today.\NTake his words as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.47,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.06,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so confused now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.36,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass! \NIt doesn't matter which, come and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.46,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.15,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He's No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.58,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.88,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:31.81,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\pos(320,390)}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.32,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.83,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,477)}I'm very strong in fighting \Nand I command Year 1 at Cromartie as their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:38.02,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But my only weak point is that I get\Ncarsickness easily, so I don't like vehicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.00,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I look like this,\NI'm actually smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:45.04,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,In middle school my deviation value was\Neasily over 60, even when I didn't study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:50.51,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why someone like me entered into\Na stupid school like Cromartie High School is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.45,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\shad0\bord0\c&H0A2B01&\fnAveria Sans\fs16\blur0.4\pos(138,44)}My home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.45,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\shad0\bord0\c&H0A2B01&\fnAveria Sans\fs16\pos(115,470)}Cromartie\N High School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.05,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,because Cromartie High School is\Nthe closest school to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.75,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very important to someone\Nwho gets motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But it takes at least fifteen minutes on foot to get\Nto school, even though I said it was the closest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.73,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So I feel too lazy to keep doing it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.67,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I'd look funny riding wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.69,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\be2\pos(316,390)}Wheels {\fscx300}-{\fscx100} a bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.50,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I'd look funny riding wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.90,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, just watching the bus made me nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.89,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I can bear it if it's only two stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.04,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,And that annoying guy isn't around here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.40,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.31,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\pos(422,392)}That annoying guy (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.64,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:24.45,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Why are you on the bus?\NTell me the reason! What's the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if you ask me the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:29.91,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your house far from school?!\NSpit it out, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.22,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes ten minutes on foot\Nfrom my house to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.79,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,and about three minutes if I use wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.28,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,That's closer than my house!\NWhy are you on the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.20,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.92,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,love transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.30,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I asked you\N to gather today is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.55,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\p1\shad0\c&HF0F0F0&\3c&H8F9B98&\bord2\pos(106,87)}m 0 0 l 108 0 108 85 0 85{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.55,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnAveria Sans\fs22\fscy95\shad0\bord0\c&H1A1A1A&\3c&HF0F0F0&\pos(105,85)}Destrade\NEmergency\NBoard\NMeeting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.57,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,to talk about Des-High's course\Nof action in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:56.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately at Des-High,\N I hear many people saying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.40,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,that we should be more aggressive\Nwith other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:05.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a very important matter\Nand I can't decide it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.45,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to do this democratically\Nand decide by majority vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.03,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.56,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually don't say serious things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.86,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll duly tell you my opinion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.53,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the situation is unstable\Ndue to the big change
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.57,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,in the balance of power between schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.64,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a good idea to\Nbe aggressive in that kind of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:28.58,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So I cast a vote for "against."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:32.78,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand fully.\NWell, any other opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.65,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.65,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, we're for it with two to one votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.92,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.89,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you have an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.76,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.16,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're not gonna say something like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:49.86,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,"this is ventriloquism\N and one of them is a puppet," are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:57.37,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if Toshiyuki Nishida is playing the role\Nof Genta Ikenaka when you're watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:02.08,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,are you gonna shout and scream, saying "He's\Nnot Genta Ikenaka, but Toshiyuki Nishida"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:05.98,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't do such a thing,\Nalthough that's a confusing example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:09.75,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've grown. Then\Nwhat kind of objection is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.19,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.66,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his hair style has been bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.46,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.49,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it bothers me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.46,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.10,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be completely open with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.77,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what democratic debate is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.74,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I want.\N I won't lose in a name-calling match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.96,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.70,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.23,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.88,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ishikawa?\NJoin the debate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.91,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:50.30,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! He always favors that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.86,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever something happens,\NI'm the only one that gets beaten up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.93,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't even know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:09:01.70,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have sort of noticed that Yamaguchi's\Nsense of humor and mine don't match, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.14,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing fine on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:11.31,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess even a delinquent may need a spirit\Nof cooperation to work well with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.79,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if ventriloquism\Nis the only way, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.25,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You wanna do ventriloquism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.19,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.83,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Paul. I'll introduce my master to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.30,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:31.60,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do? I'm Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Paul. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.37,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? My voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.31,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming out delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.54,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,That technique?!\N How are you able to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.89,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't a technique that only he could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.84,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.61,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please make me your pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.09,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Then let's go and\Nbuy you one straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.59,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.52,Typeset,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\pos(316,390)}Next day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.03,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do? I'm David.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.57,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my new partner.\N He's looking forward to getting to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:09.14,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting's okay,\N and feel the sorrow well... just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:11.25,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think better of you, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.28,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally understand, Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.08,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth spending 150,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.38,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.55,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted was that spirit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.18,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that I have to rethink\Nthe ranking of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.27,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.05,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully! I have\Nan announcement to make to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.53,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the new No. 2 from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.53,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to getting to know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.73,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that we can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:44.07,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does he think it cost?
