Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.02,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.66,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:41.16,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beginning to think that\NI'd be better off if I say
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.26,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll tell you about the next episode."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.07,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll try my best to do it as I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.47,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(60,470)}I'm Mick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.07,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(60,470)}I'm Paul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.00,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(60,470)}I'm David!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.07,Dialogue etc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(60,470)}Four of us together\N is a puppet trio!
